        <h1>Performance of logging</h1>
            <p>
			Experimental results are listed below in units of <b>micro-seconds
			</b>. Measurements were done on a AMD Athlon 2200+ running Linux
			Mandrake 10.0.
            </p>
 			<p>
			<table border="1">
			<caption align="top">Version 0.9.6</caption>
				<tr>
					<th>Layout</th>
					<th>NullAppender</th>
					<th>FileAppender</th>
					<th>FileAppender (no flush)</th>
					<th>AsyncAppender (no flush)</th>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td>SimpleLayout</td>
					<td>4</td>
					<td>12</td>
					<td>11</td>
					<td>24</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td>PatternLayout "%p - %m%n"</td>
					<td>5</td>
					<td>12</td>
					<td>5</td>
					<td>15</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td>PatternLayout "%-5p - %m%n"</td>
					<td>6</td>
					<td>NA</td>
					<td>NA</td>
					<td>NA</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td>TTCCLayout/RELATIVE</td>
